{"tid":2214774,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"單身巴打百年歸老遺產除咗捐仲可以點","createTime":"2020-09-23T13:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T03:10:36.000Z","uid":373544,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"109df3998dc8ecb42a03b01ecd5515bf653a0636","tid":2214774,"uid":373544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"講緊知自己唔會同人結婚的話 又有物業揸手<br />\n兄姊又大過自己好多應該走先 佢哋又冇仔女如果唔係都可以俾下班細路<br />\n咁唔通咁益啲冇聯絡嘅疏堂親戚咩真係<br />\n我自己都唔細 依家拍親拖都feel到一係對方玩玩下一係自己求其搵條女陪自己咁 注定孤獨終老<br />\n咁死咗之後啲物業究竟益邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分享下少少 以前有個舊同事一早死老豆老母 結果呀嫲定婆走嗰陣層樓就俾曬佢 （加多利山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）無啦啦就多咗咁大筆資產 <br />\n<br />\n又試過以前中學同學出嚟聚先知<br />\n有個女同學2x歲時自己單身<br />\n有個好錫佢嘅中學呀sir又係單身寡佬 <br />\n個呀sir就喺條女2x歲時自己病撚死咗<br />\n點知聽聞個呀sir在生時就轉咗兩層樓個名俾條女<br />\n好似係遺囑唔可以就咁訂話俾曬條女 定係會引其他親人爭拗之類 就一早轉咗名先<br />\n總之佢咁就收咗兩層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知個呀sir係有幾唔想益啲親生兄弟先咁<br />\n過咗好幾年中同聚會先有人踢爆佢<br />\n嗰刻係我咁大個仔最覺得做女人真係著數啲嘅一刻<br />\n試下當年嗰個好學痴身活潑嘅唔係條青春中上學生妹 而係一個學生哥<br />\n個呀sir撚會咁錫佢錫到送埋樓俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然條女自己本身都係選擇性單身 又叻女嗰啲女人嚟<br />\n但後生女無啦啦咁收兩層樓真係生活可以好唔同<br />\n尤其近年樓價升到咁<br />\n個呀sir啲親生兄弟就好似淨係分到佢留低啲股票同儲蓄<br />\n<br />\n都係知呢件事之後先開始諗老咗自己啲遺產應該俾邊個<br />\n我臨死應該冇學生妹可以俾我送物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識條女嘅勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4633897e67edfae8f9f420171b4809bf48c67c28","tid":2214774,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"送比我當濟貧 助你上天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0ef3be4c81cbdece3844eb211d751146e0cb4b","tid":2214774,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4633897e67edfae8f9f420171b4809bf48c67c28","tid":2214774,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"送比我當濟貧 助你上天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"利申 非絲打<br />\n有大賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76fb4a0259d83ec1af9482c47224925a330b949","tid":2214774,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"逆按揭拎埋舊錢玩哂佢囉 我身邊有準備退休嘅同事咁做"},{"pid":"0a056df4c776fcb848f4c6fb6c8e108cc8f3be26","tid":2214774,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"有塊西分身家是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b4e3c65cad4681978f0b7fe8a09b1f19a8dbd0","tid":2214774,"uid":156812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊點樣喺死之前用晒啲錢<br />\n一蚊都唔想分比其他人"},{"pid":"ebe917819a9a6aa5755961bfa7934453efcd1f9c","tid":2214774,"uid":373544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b4e3c65cad4681978f0b7fe8a09b1f19a8dbd0","tid":2214774,"uid":156812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊點樣喺死之前用晒啲錢<br />\n一蚊都唔想分比其他人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇結婚？"},{"pid":"89760583541efaa807e0c5246d6abab760b78bc5","tid":2214774,"uid":373544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a056df4c776fcb848f4c6fb6c8e108cc8f3be26","tid":2214774,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"有塊西分身家是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/